PrecisAuthority for the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development and other Ministers of the Crown to consider the INNU PEOPLE living in the Labrador communities of Sheshatshiu and Davis Inlet as if they were Status Indians residing on "reserve land", for the purpose of providing them with social services and programs.
